    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/0d37cf51d6a8397076511b53625dc2cc.avif?t=1770485289\" width=616 height=74 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dragon-riding extraction ARPG with castle building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragonhold is a mission-based dragon riding ARPG. Take on dangerous excursions across the war-torn Azarkeen region, fighting on dragonback and on foot to seize loot and relics. Then <strong>extract back to your castle island</strong>, where you expand your town, craft gear, and upgrade your warriors for the next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each mission is a risk–reward run: push deeper for better rewards, or extract early to secure what you’ve found. Play fully <strong>solo</strong> or team up in <strong>online co-op</strong>; your progress and castle carry across both.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragonhold is NOT always online. You can run a dedicated server yourself, or play on many freely provided official servers. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Ride and fight on dragons</strong> – Soar over battlefields, strafe enemies with fire, then dive into brutal close-quarters combat as a dragon rider.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mission-based extraction loop</strong> – Choose your mission, hunt for loot and materials, then extract safely or risk  going deeper.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Rebuild Dragonhold castle</strong> – Restore a ruined stronghold and surrounding town; unlock vendors, crafting stations, and new progression systems as you rebuild.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft and upgrade</strong> – Forge weapons, armor, and arcane relics. Grow your dragon’s power and your own build with skills and gear.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bosses and elite encounters</strong> – Take on challenging bosses both on dragonback and on foot, learning patterns and coordinating with allies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/65dedf0328e012b58c92212e4b2cdce5.avif?t=1770485289\" width=616 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take to the skies on a mighty dragon and unleash fiery attacks on your enemies. Explore a vast enchanted realm and save the people of Azarkeen. Unleash deadly abilities and magical powers to prevent a corrupt holy war spreading across the world. Restore the balance in spectacular third-person action in solo or multiplayer modes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/19abe1a26dc0a334adc21e9eb9051db5.poster.avif?t=1770485289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/19abe1a26dc0a334adc21e9eb9051db5.webm?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/19abe1a26dc0a334adc21e9eb9051db5.mp4?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play solo or with friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragonhold is <strong>fully playable solo from start to finish</strong> – you don’t need other players or a constant online population to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play offline / privately</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Host your own dedicated server </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Or join freely provided official servers for co-op sessions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-op is there if you want it; the entire experience can be enjoyed as a single-player ARPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/1d47c41772fae20394ef72abe168e042.avif?t=1770485289\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/5bbbfe4ddd9e51b33028cdc5d4a5cc19.poster.avif?t=1770485289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/5bbbfe4ddd9e51b33028cdc5d4a5cc19.webm?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/5bbbfe4ddd9e51b33028cdc5d4a5cc19.mp4?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/f30965f30b815cc22f029990ec49babe.avif?t=1770485289\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/09e290032195e9adc17600a9bc98dece.poster.avif?t=1770485289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/09e290032195e9adc17600a9bc98dece.webm?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/09e290032195e9adc17600a9bc98dece.mp4?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/f9f6f25ae6d935ade682bb90dbd55f99.avif?t=1770485289\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/214d5ad1726bc2c92f6db82499eede44.poster.avif?t=1770485289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/214d5ad1726bc2c92f6db82499eede44.webm?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/214d5ad1726bc2c92f6db82499eede44.mp4?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Are you ready to become a member of the legendary Boundless Order, harnessing the power of dragons and etching your name into the annals of history? Your destiny awaits in Dragonhold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/cae818851c4cc5805e9cb36411deaa27.poster.avif?t=1770485289\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/cae818851c4cc5805e9cb36411deaa27.webm?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1510330/extras/cae818851c4cc5805e9cb36411deaa27.mp4?t=1770485289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
